1 - Database Storage for Unique Mixer Series
    - Retrievable based on link and passcode
    - Passcode properly (rotating) salted/hashed/etc

2 - Allow Users to Sign up for Unique Mixers, collecting:
    - Group Name
    - Group Size
    - Dates Available to Host
    - Dates Available to Attend
    - Email

3 - Automated Emails:
    - On Sign up, Email participant of their enrollment stats (dates they said they could host, attnend, etc)
    - 1 Week Prior to Event, send reminder to Host with their Attendees CCed.

- Automated Email Scheduling:
    - Allow Admins/Hosts/Attendees to determine how often/if they receive email notifications.

